ila if preferred.","When cherries aren't in season, you can use frozen or jarred cherries, or substitute cherries with strawberries. If using jarred cherries in sugar syrup, you may want to reduce the amount of sugar in this recipe.","Add additional ice to dilute the cocktail to desired taste.","Cherry syrup can be made up to 1 week in advance and stored in the refrigerator."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","25m","8 portions"]}